          </h1>\n362 |               <p className=\"text-[11px] md:text-xs text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed font-sans max-w-md\">\n363 |                 No simulated preview session is currently associated with your browser client. To access the interactive sandbox of GFF AI, authorize your token.\n364 |               </p>\n365 |             </div>\n366 | \n367 |             {/* Countdown redirect bar */}\n368 |             <div className=\"space-y-1.5 bg-zinc-950/40 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5\">\n369 |               <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-500 tracking-wider\">\n370 |                 <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n371 |                   <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 text-red-500 animate-spin\" />\n372 |                   STANDBY: REDIRECTING TO IDENTITY GATEWAY\n373 |                 </span>\n374 |                 <span className=\"font-bold\">{countdown}S</span>\n375 |               </div>\n376 |               <div className=\"h-1 bg-zinc-900 border border-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n377 |                 <div \n378 |                   className=\"h-full bg-red-500/80 transition-all duration-1000 ease-linear\" \n379 |                   style={{ width: `${pct}%` }} \n380 |                 />\n381 |               </div>\n382 |               <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 pt-2\">\n383 |                 <button \n384 |                   onClick={() => router.push(type === \"admin\" ? \"/admin/login\" : \"/portal/login\")}\n385 |                   className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg bg-white hover:bg-zinc-200 text-black text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-white\"\n386 |                 >\n387 |                   <Fingerprint className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n388 |                   <span>Authenticate Manually</span>\n389 |                 </button>\n390 |               </div>\n391 |             </div>\n392 | \n393 |             {/* Simulated Workspace Quick Launch Grid */}\n394 |             <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n395 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n396 |                 <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">\n397 |                   Quick-Authenticate Sandbox Simulation\n398 |                 </span>\n399 |                 <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-cyan-400/60 font-semibold select-none\">\n400 |                   DEVELOPER BYPASS\n401 |                 </span>\n402 |               </div>\n403 |               <p className=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">\n404 |                 Skip full credential checks and force-bind a mock clearance identity to instantly traverse this portal sector:\n405 |               </p>\n406 | \n407 |               <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n408 |                 {simProfiles.map((roleId) => {\n409 |                   const meta = ROLE_METADATA[roleId];\n410 |                   const isNegotiating = negotiating === roleId;\n411 | \n412 |                   return (\n413 |                     <button\n414 |                       key={roleId}\n415 |                       onClick={() => handleBypass(roleId)}\n416 |                       disabled={negotiating !== null}\n417 |                       className=\"text-left p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between h-36 cursor-pointer hover:border-white/15 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-1 focus-visible:outline-cyan-500 disabled:opacity-40\"\n418 |                       style={{\n419 |                         boxShadow: isNegotiating ? `0 0 24px ${meta.glowColor}` : \"none\",\n420 